
Epoch 3/10
176/176 [==============================] - 83s - loss: 1.4960 - acc: 0.5148 - val_loss: 1.1218 - val_acc: 0.6562
Epoch 4/10
176/176 [==============================] - 82s - loss: 1.4529 - acc: 0.5319 - val_loss: 1.1899 - val_acc: 0.6068
Epoch 5/10
176/176 [==============================] - 84s - loss: 1.4605 - acc: 0.5237 - val_loss: 1.1750 - val_acc: 0.6106
Epoch 6/10
176/176 [==============================] - 83s - loss: 1.4577 - acc: 0.5184 - val_loss: 1.1802 - val_acc: 0.6198
Epoch 7/10
176/176 [==============================] - 83s - loss: 1.4592 - acc: 0.5221 - val_loss: 1.2200 - val_acc: 0.5964
Epoch 8/10
176/176 [==============================] - 82s - loss: 1.4374 - acc: 0.5287 - val_loss: 1.1175 - val_acc: 0.6168
